data.title: Omnisphere, Keyscape, Trilian, Stylus RMX
data.text:
Omnisphere - Power Synth

Omnisphere is the flagship synthesizer of Spectrasonics® - an instrument of extraordinary power and versatility. This award-winning plugin brings many different types of synthesis together into one amazing-sounding instrument that will inspire a lifetime of exploration.

Keyscape - Collector Keyboards

KEYSCAPE™ is an extraordinary new virtual instrument featuring the largest selection of collector keyboards in the world. Ten years in the making, the 36 rare and sought-after keyboards were carefully restored and then deeply multisampled to inspire you to PLAY!
